    <section id="2" noNumber="0" sautDePagePdf="0">
      <title>Detailed Description</title>
      <paragraph type="important" sautDePagePdf="0">The Qt XML Patterns module provides support for XPath, <link href="xmlprocessing.html">XQuery</link>, XSLT and XML Schema validation.</paragraph>
      <paragraph type="important" sautDePagePdf="0">The <link href="qtxmlpatterns-index.html">Qt XML Patterns</link> module provides support for XPath, <link href="xmlprocessing.html">XQuery</link>, XSLT and XML Schema validation.</paragraph>
      <paragraph type="important" sautDePagePdf="0">To include the definitions of the module's classes, use the following directive:</paragraph>
      <code langage="other">
        #include &lt;QtXmlPatterns&gt;
      </code>
